                  <accMat>
                     <p>On the fly-leaf <name type="person" key="ArnMag001">Árni Magnússon</name>
                        noted the names of the sagas in the manuscript. <name type="person"
                           key="MagEin005">Magnus Einarsson</name> wrote underneath: <q
                           xml:lang="is">Úr bokum er eg feck af S<ex>ira</ex> Olafe Gisla syne <lb/>
                            Hofe i Vopnafirde.</q>, a sentence that originated from Árni Magnússon
                        and can also be found in <ref type="ms" target="#AM02-0349-is">AM 349 4to</ref> and other
                        manuscripts.</p>
